that\nthe speed of the inlabru inversion, which include a rigorous estimation of\nuncertainty, will enable a deeper exploration of how to use ETAS robustly for\nseismicity modelling and operational earthquake forecasting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 17:46:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 13:59:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-16"}
