 hint that $f(red)$ may\nstart to increase again because the metal-rich GCs also become dominated by\naccreted systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 19:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
