ars that in super-Eddington AGN, as for\nlower Eddington ratio AGN, the X-ray corona is controlled by pair production\nand annihilation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 19:00:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
