en compared to those PIs generated by three\nstate-of-the-art neural-network-based methods. In other words, our method was\nshown to produce higher-quality PIs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2022 05:03:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 18:55:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-03"}
