t least 2.1$\\times$ for all SNRs in terms\nof network throughput, demonstrating quick and reliable data aggregation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2022 13:48:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
