optimal performance when SNR $\\geq$ 6 dB for two-user\nLDPC-coded AirComp, demonstrating the advantage of digital AirComp in\nphase-asynchronous multi-user OFDM systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2022 14:19:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
